						               													<description>!!!ATTENTION!!!&amp;#10;Special unique climbing equipment available at ESSEN SPIEL 2018.&amp;#10;Use the power of Mystical TIBETAN POTION or magical FLYING CARPET to claim your victory.&amp;#10;Special tiles set free of charge for each purchased copy of ROLL &amp;amp; WALL.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Provided with all the necessary equipment like good shoes, ropes, and a chalk bag &amp;mdash; as well as some lucky charms in your rucksack (just in case) &amp;mdash; you are taking part in a climbing competition. Your aim is to become a world-class climber by reaching the top of the mountain first and getting one up on your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roll &amp;amp; Wall is a fast-paced family dice racing game, for 2 to 5 players, in which you try to climb as high as you can by using dice. During your turn, you have six dice and you have to decide how many of them you want to use for each step. Climbing up requires to roll dice with matching or higher value than those printed on your chosen space on the board. You can take a risk and try to roll &amp;quot;4&amp;quot; or higher by using only one die or play it safe and use three dice. Used dice become unavailable until your next round, so you should choose wisely. Throughout the race, climbers can use handy items which they picked up at the beginning of the game. Special amulets, energy bars, and professional climbing equipment help players to reach the top faster or (if you are a mischievous rascal) to make climbing harder for other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game contains three modular two-sided race tracks which allow for the track to be changed at the beginning of each game. Inside the box you will find an awesome cardboard dice tower, making rolling the dice a much more charming experience. Gather friends and family and check if you got what it takes to become master climber!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
